                                            <div class="b-title">3月26日第二批驰援意大利的324箱物资发出</div>
                                            <div class="b-time">2020-03-26</div>
                                            <div class="b-discription">
                                                3月26日黎明56箱医用外科口罩14.1万个，268箱防护服10375件从石家庄进德公益装车送往北京，将从北京运往米兰。                                                <button class="am-btn am-btn-danger am-btn-xs" data-am-modal="{target: '#my-popup-6'}">查看详情</button>
                                                <div class="am-popup" id="my-popup-6">
                                                    <div class="am-popup-inner">
                                                        <div class="am-popup-hd">
                                                            <h4 class="am-popup-title">3月26日第二批驰援意大利的324箱物资发出</h4>
                                                            <span data-am-modal-close
                                                                  class="am-close">&times;</span>
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="am-popup-bd">
                                                            <p>3月26日黎明56箱医用外科口罩14.1万个，268箱防护服10375件从石家庄进德公益装车送往北京，将从北京运往米兰。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/Editor/Test/2020/04/031585892682581661.jpg"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/Editor/2020-03-27/5e7dbe7a7a70f.png" alt="" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/Editor/2020-03-27/5e7dbe98be9bb.png" alt="" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/Uploads/Editor/2020-03-27/5e7dbf35d3e9d.png" alt="" style="box-sizing: border-box; vertical-align: middle; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, FreeSans, Arimo, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;wenquanyi micro hei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p>                                              